title: The Cheesecake Factory
seo_title: The Cheesecake Factory in Waikiki | Things to do in Waikiki
seo_description: Located a short walk from the Aqua Waikiki Pearl is this iconic American restaurant. The menu is large, but save room for dessert: their cheesecake is a must
contents_1: Located a short walk from the Pearl Hotel Waikiki is this popular American sit-down restaurant.
